    "_cissia_note": "Cissia is gear-CR / passive-fed-CDMG (Festering Venom self-grants +50% CRIT DMG, off-screen combat) so her CRIT DMG goalpost is LOW (110+) and CRIT Rate is the gear stat (50-57 w/ signature, no mechanical cap). Disk 6 main is ENERGY REGEN, not ATK%: her Core Passive scales squad DEF-Ignore with ER above 1.4, maxing at 12.88% DEF-Ignore at ER 3.68 (1.4 + 19 steps of 0.52% per 0.12 ER) — that's the Energy Regen `cap`. Prydwen 2.7.",
